quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  48,18,"Gom…óii Allah welano gom…óim…ďe …ďen, tuma …ďe ahondiraynoo e maa…óa ka ley lekki kin. O anndi ko woni kon ka …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, O jippini dee∆īere nden e ma…ď…ďe, O warjorii…ďe uddital …ďadiingal"
  48,19,"e konu-heyri …óuu…óundi ndi …ďe henndotoo. Allah siforii wonnde Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  48,20,"Allah fodii on konu-heyri …óuu…óundi ndi henndoto…óon, O yaccinani on ndii …óoo, O suri juu…óe yim…ďe …ďen e mo'on, fii yo wonu maande wonannde gom…óim…ďe …ďen, O fewnira on laawol focciingol"
  48,21,"E wonndi goo ndi on ha…ótanaali taho, Allah kan no hu…ďindii ndi. Allah siforii wonnde ha…ótan…óo kala huunde"
  48,22,"Hay si yeddu…ďe …ďen ha…ďiino on, …ďe huccintinayno …ďabbe ma…ď…ďe …óen, refti …ďe he…ďataano gi…óo wanaa ballao"
  48,23,"∆äum ko sunna Alla fe∆ī∆īunoo…óo ko adii. A he…ďantaa laawol Alla ngol, mbattiigu"
  48,24,"Ko Kanko woni suran…óo on juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e mo'on, e suru…óo juu…óe mon …óen e ma…ď…ďe, ka aynde Makka, …ďaawo O foolnude on e ma…ď…ďe. Allah siforii wonnde Reenu…óo ko golloton kon"
  48,25,"Ko …ďen woni ko yeddi, …ďe faddii on e Juurlirde Hormorde nden, […ďe ha…ói] neldaari ndin nde ndi yottotoo nokku mayri. Si wanaano sabu wor…ďe gom…óim…ďe e rew…ďe gom…óim…ďe …ďe on anndataano haa ha…ďon …ďe, bakkaatu he…ďa on e fee ma…ď…ďe, ko aldaa e anndugol... fii yo Allah naadu e yurmeende Makko nden, on mo O muuyani. Si …ďe senndondir-no [e gom…óim…ďe …ďen], ko pellet, Men leptirayno yeddu…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe, lepte muusu…óe"
  48,26,"Tuma nde …ďeya yeddu…ďe wa…óunoo ka …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe jinngo, jinngo majjiyanke...Allah jippini dee∆īere Makko nden e dow Nulaa…óo Makko on e gom…óim…ďe …ďen, O fawi …ďe konngol gom…óal, …ďe woni …ďur…ďe jojjude e hanndude e maggol. Allah siforii Anndugol kala huunde"